"""
Abstract superclass of types that support comparison via `<` and `=`.
Subclasses must implement `<` and `=`; derived comparison methods
(`max:`, `min:`, `between:and:`) are provided by the Comparable trait.

```test
5 max: 3 >>> 5
3 min: 5 >>> 3
5 between: 1 and: 10 >>> true
0 between: 1 and: 10 >>> false
```
"""
Magnitude subclass: Object
  include: Comparable
